I"ù<h2 id="about-this">ABOUT THIS</h2>

<p>The Science Pulse is sponsored by the International Center for Journalists with support from the Knight Foundation, and was developed by the data-driven agency Volt Data Lab to help inform journalists around scientific topics, especially for the fight against the coronavirus pandemic.</p>

<h2 id="methodology">METHODOLOGY</h2>

<p>All the profiles of scientists, experts, physicians, organisations and scientific initiatives were compiled by Pulseâ€™s development team, and where based on the biographies displayed in their profiles at the time of collection. One way method used was identifying users with profiles verified by Twitter and checking people who they follow. We also used Twitter lists of scientists.</p>
